(secondQuint)Integrating Advance Care Planning Into a Pre-Dialysis Educational Program.

 Mixed methods study that will use qualitative methods to develop an ACP educational intervention.

 This intervention will be randomized among patients with advanced chronic kidney disease who are referred for pre-dialysis education.

.

 Integrating Advance Care Planning Into a Pre-Dialysis Educational Program@highlight

The goals of this work will be to 1) develop an ACP educational intervention that will be integrated into a standard pre-dialysis program and 2) evaluate its preliminary efficacy on increased use of ACP among patients with advanced CKD and their families.

